Saudi Arabia to Approve Mortgage Law Soon, Arab News Reports

-- B y   Z a i n a b   F a t t a h
-- 
2011-03-07T05:27:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/saudi-arabia-to-approve-mortgage-law-soon-arab-news-reports.html
  Saudi Arabia  will soon approve a
mortgage law, Arab News reported, citing Shoura Council Chairman
Abdullah Al-Asheikh.  A six-member committee is studying the details of the draft
law, he was cited as saying by the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
